prompts.frontCover: A charming, flat 2D cartoon illustration of a slightly frazzled, very fluffy brown squirrel attempting to balance a wobbly, towering stack of acorns, with a few acorns comically falling mid-air. The squirrel has wide, expressive eyes and a determined but slightly panicked expression. At the very top of the acorn pile, a single birthday candle with a flickering flame is precariously perched. The entire scene is rendered in a soft, lighthearted watercolor painting style, featuring beautiful, flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds on a subtle paper texture. In the center of the design, the words "happy birthday" are elegantly written in a beautiful, readable, dark brown handwritten cursive script. The background is a simple, clean wash of pale blue and soft green, suggesting a whimsical outdoor setting without distracting from the main scene.
